  <brief_title>Atorvastatin for HAART Suboptimal Responders</brief_title>
  <official_title>Use of Atorvastatin as Adjuvant Therapy Among Suboptimal Responders to Antiretroviral Therapy in an African Cohort of HAART-treated Adults: A Randomised Controlled Trial</official_title>
